          <div class="philosophy">
            <h3>Our Philosophy</h3>
            <p>Don't start from scratch. Find an open-source project, a template, an asset pack—anything that gives you a foundation—and build something Catholic from it. Fork it, extend it, reskin it.</p>
            <p>What you make here becomes part of that same commons. Future jams build on your work. The body of Catholic games grows.</p>
