          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Can I work on a team?</summary>
            <p>Yes, any size. Find teammates beforehand or go solo—your choice.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>What if I want to start from scratch?</summary>
            <p>That's fine. We encourage building on existing work, but it's not required.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How do I submit?</summary>
